# 7. Why Kadane Works

At every position:

```text
Best subarray ending at i
=
either

current element

OR

extend previous best
```

Formula:

```java
dp[i] =
max(
arr[i],
dp[i-1] + arr[i]
)
```

Kadane simply stores:

```text
Only previous state
```

instead of full DP array.

Thus:

```text
Dynamic Programming Optimization
```

